name: EXPERIMENTAL FILM 4: "CIRCE - the witch"
description:
This is new 'concept sketch' from a digital art COLLAB with myself
and @filtnerlii the creator of 100 Goobers.

This is about CIRCE the witch who tried to enchant
Ulysses and his men to remain on her island forever.

The images are photos and paintings and digital collage.

The face you see is the statue Elizabeth Montgomery in Salem MA.

There is an irony here -- but it's still dark.

Perhaps this is my scariest one yet?
Pretty good since HALLOWEEN is only one week away.

Grab these sketches cheap because the finished pieces will be priced higher.

Happy collecting!
